metadata.name: Platinum Membership
metadata.description: CanvasArtists Platinum memberships offer access to the most exclusive NFT artists as well as the opportunity to purchase the physical artwork associated with the NFT.  In addition, our platinum members receive white glove customer service, invitations to live events featuring our platinum artists,  a voice in the future of CanvasArtists and access to our crypto experts.  We are limiting memberships to 55 in total.
